<seg id="67">Speaker (Hon. Joe Enook) (interpretation): Mr. Quassa, can you say the opening prayer, please.</seg>
<seg id="68">Speaker (interpretation): Good afternoon, Premier, Members, and Nunavummiut who are listening to the radio broadcast and watching the televised proceedings. Welcome to your committee.</seg>
