<seg id="135">Member’s Statement 097 – 4(1): Kitikmeot Youth Empowerment (Qirngnuq)</seg>
<seg id="136">Mr. Qirngnuq (interpretation): Thank you, Mr. Speaker.</seg>
<seg id="137">What I’m going to be talking about is something that is very good for young people to think about and to plan for their future.</seg>
<seg id="138">I rise today to share some good news with my colleagues.</seg>
<seg id="139">Mr. Speaker, I am pleased to inform the House that Inuit youth from across the Kitikmeot will be gathering in Cambridge Bay next week for the 2018 Kitikmeot Youth Empowerment Conference.</seg>
